  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You wake up on a mysterious beach, where beautiful but somewhat unrealistic events take place. A first-person riddle-solving escape game to uncover the truth.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just walking along the beach will only make you go in a loop, but the scene will change little by little depending on your actions. Solve the mystery and escape from this world.<strong> </strong><br> <strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/97951e6c99e019778a402008d1b6ceeb.avif?t=1747976473\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras_big/97951e6c99e019778a402008d1b6ceeb.avif?t=1747976473 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Examine objects on the beach</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are various objects on the beach that can be examined to progress the story and solve new mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/9e4cb3e18288155fdb96d7d8b0ce43c3.avif?t=1747976473\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras_big/9e4cb3e18288155fdb96d7d8b0ce43c3.avif?t=1747976473 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use the items you get.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Items you explore and obtain may be used somewhere. If you use them in various places, you will advance the story somewhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/acf739b330cf3f90393255377b649493.avif?t=1747976473\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras_big/acf739b330cf3f90393255377b649493.avif?t=1747976473 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Changing Phases</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story progresses to solve riddles in various locations, not only on the beach.<strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/c9d820ab6a322b1948d37e625db6a049.poster.avif?t=1747976473\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/c9d820ab6a322b1948d37e625db6a049.webm?t=1747976473\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/c9d820ab6a322b1948d37e625db6a049.mp4?t=1747976473\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*All videos and screenshots are under development.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You wake up on a mysterious beach, where beautiful but somewhat unrealistic events take place. A first-person riddle-solving escape game to uncover the truth.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just walking along the beach will only make you go in a loop, but the scene will change little by little depending on your actions. Solve the mystery and escape from this world.<strong> </strong><br> <strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/97951e6c99e019778a402008d1b6ceeb.avif?t=1747976473\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras_big/97951e6c99e019778a402008d1b6ceeb.avif?t=1747976473 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Examine objects on the beach</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are various objects on the beach that can be examined to progress the story and solve new mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/9e4cb3e18288155fdb96d7d8b0ce43c3.avif?t=1747976473\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras_big/9e4cb3e18288155fdb96d7d8b0ce43c3.avif?t=1747976473 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use the items you get.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Items you explore and obtain may be used somewhere. If you use them in various places, you will advance the story somewhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/acf739b330cf3f90393255377b649493.avif?t=1747976473\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras_big/acf739b330cf3f90393255377b649493.avif?t=1747976473 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Changing Phases</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story progresses to solve riddles in various locations, not only on the beach.<strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/c9d820ab6a322b1948d37e625db6a049.poster.avif?t=1747976473\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/c9d820ab6a322b1948d37e625db6a049.webm?t=1747976473\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340240/extras/c9d820ab6a322b1948d37e625db6a049.mp4?t=1747976473\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*All videos and screenshots are under development.</p>",
